uk.co.strangeskies.reflection

Class TypeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.strangeskies.reflection.TypeVisitor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RecursiveTypeVisitor

    public abstract class TypeVisitor
extends Object
    A visitor to allow types to be dealt with as their specific class without the need for manual type checking and casting. Types can be visited recursively by calling visit(Collection) or visit(Type...) within each implementation of the abstract visiting methods.
